        <h2>Small Tablets Grid</h2>
        <p>By default, the grid columns will collapse into individual rows when the viewport is below 768 pixles wide. Using the <code>small-tablet</code> modifier, you can specify columns to maintain their grid structure until the viewport width falls below 480 pixels.</p>
