        <h2>Re-ordering</h2>
        <p>Re-ordering or "source ordering" is an especially useful modifier when you want content on the right on larger viewports, but on top on mobile viewports. This can be especially applicable when optimizing content for search engines and accessibility. For example, you can relatively adjust columns positioning by using <code>right-one</code> or <code>left-three</code>.</p>
